MITgcmUV Getting Started
========================

o Introduction

o Install
  tar -xvf ...
  cd tools
  genmake.dec
  cd ../bin
  ln -s ../tools/Makefile.dec makefile
  make depend
  make
  setenv PARALLEL 1
  ../exe/barrier

o Running
  
  - Inout files
    eedata
    data

  - Serial execution

  - Parallel execution. Threads
    nSx, nSy
    setenv PARALLEL n
    nTx=2, nTy=2

  - Parallel execution. MPI
    mPx, nPy
    dmpirun

  - Parallel execution. Hybrid

o References
